review 1: Good place for relax and chill with friends and familly! The food was  tasteless. we ordered margarita pizza , mix fried , grilled chicken, and spagethi carbonara. The service was good, just need bit improvement for the food :)

review 4:
Very nice Indonesian food. Fresh fish and variety of western food such as pizza, pasta and burger. I would recommend the Indonesian food.

The staff is amazing. Prices are legit.
